recipes.title: Chicken Salad
recipes.description: A light and refreshing salad with yogurt dressing.
recipes.instructions: Boil the chicken, slice vegetables, mix all together and serve chilled.

recipes.title: Chocolate Cake
recipes.instructions: Mix all ingredients and bake at 180°C for 30 minutes.

recipes.title: Pasta Carbonara
recipes.description: Classic Italian pasta dish with creamy sauce.
recipes.instructions: Cook pasta, fry pancetta, whisk eggs with cheese, mix all and season with pepper.

recipes.title: Greek Salad
recipes.description: Fresh salad with feta cheese and olives.
recipes.instructions: Chop vegetables, add feta and olives, drizzle with olive oil and serve.

recipes.title: Pancakes
recipes.instructions: Mix batter, pour on pan, cook until golden brown on both sides, serve with syrup.

recipes.title: Vegetable Soup
recipes.instructions: Chop vegetables, cook in broth until tender, season with salt and pepper.
